    • javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.TagSupport

    TableTag

    public abstract class AbstractTableTag
extends javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.BodyTagSupport
implements javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.DynamicAttributes

    Superclass of TableTag containing:

    • tag attributes declaration (note that all the corresponding setters are in the TableTag
    • helper attributes and methods used to initialize the table

    • Method Detail

      • processIteration

        protected int processIteration()
                        throws javax.servlet.jsp.JspException

        Process the iteration over the collection of data.

        Note that no iteration is required when using an AJAX source.

        Returns:
        EVAL_BODY_BUFFERED if some data remain in the Java Collection, SKIP_BODY otherwise.
        Throws:
        javax.servlet.jsp.JspException - if something went wrong during the row id generation.

      • getRowId

        protected String getRowId()
                   throws javax.servlet.jsp.JspException
        Return the row id using prefix, base and suffix. Prefix and sufix are just prepended and appended strings. Base is extracted from the current iterated object.
        Returns:
        return the row id using prefix, base and suffix.
        Throws:
        javax.servlet.jsp.JspException - is the rowIdBase doesn't have a corresponding property accessor method.

      • setupHtmlGeneration

        protected int setupHtmlGeneration()
                           throws javax.servlet.jsp.JspException
        Set up the HTML table generation.
        Returns:
        allways EVAL_PAGE to keep evaluating the page.
        Throws:
        javax.servlet.jsp.JspException - if something went wrong during the processing.

      • setupExport

        protected int setupExport()
                   throws javax.servlet.jsp.JspException
        Set up the export properties, before the filter intercepts the response.
        Returns:
        always SKIP_PAGE, because the export filter will override the response with the exported data instead of displaying the page.
        Throws:
        javax.servlet.jsp.JspException - if something went wrong during export.
